Privacy Policy
Kamrej Apps
("we," "our," or "us") operates the
Beauty Camera - AI Photo Editor
application (the "App"). This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect the personal information you provide while using the App.
1. Information We Collect
Device Information:
We may collect details about your device, such as model, operating system, and unique identifiers.
Usage Data
:
We collect information about how you interact with the App to improve functionality and performance.
In-App Purchases:
We collect and store information related to your transactions within the App to provide the purchased features and services.
2. Permissions
Camera & Gallery Access:
Required for capturing and editing photos and videos within the App.
Storage Access:
Required for saving edited photos or videos.
Network Access:
Internet access may be required for displaying ads, performing analytics, or connecting to third-party services.
3. How We Use Your Information
To allow you to capture and edit photos or videos using the App.
To manage and process your in-app purchases.
To improve the App’s functionality and user experience.
To serve relevant advertisements through third-party networks.
4. Third-Party Services
We may use third-party services for analytics, advertising, and other features:
Google Analytics
:
Used to collect anonymized data about how the App is used and to improve performance.
AdMob by Google:
Used for displaying ads that may collect information about your interaction with them.
5. Data Security
We take data security seriously and use appropriate technical measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access or disclosure.
6. Data Retention
We retain personal data for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this policy.
7. Your Rights Under GDPR
If you are a resident of the European Economic Area (EEA), you have certain data protection rights under the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR):
Right to Access:
You have the right to request access to the personal information we may have about you.
Right to Rectification:
You have the right to request the correction of inaccurate data.
Right to Erasure:
You may request the deletion of your personal data.
Right to Restrict Processing:
You can request limitations on how your data is processed.
Right to Data Portability:
You may request a copy of your personal data in a structured format.
Right to Object:
You can object to the processing of your data, especially in cases involving ads.
This Privacy Policy (“Privacy Policy”) is an integral part of our End User License Agreement (“EULA”) and governs the processing and transfer of personal data collected or processed by Kamrej Apps. Any capitalized terms not defined herein shall have the meaning ascribed to them in the EULA.
8. CCPA Privacy
If you are a resident of California, you have the following rights under the California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA):
Right to Notice:
You must be notified which categories of personal data are collected and the purposes for which they are used.
Right to Access/Request:
You may request and obtain information regarding the disclosure of your personal data over the last 12 months.
Right to Say No to Sale:
You may request that your personal data not be sold to third parties.
Right to Delete:
You may request the deletion of personal data collected in the last 12 months.
Right to Non-Discrimination:
You will not be discriminated against for exercising your rights under the CCPA.
For any requests under the CCPA, you may email or contact us directly, and we will respond within 45 days.
9. Detailed Information on the Processing of Your Personal Data
Service providers have access to your personal data only to perform their tasks on our behalf and are obligated not to disclose or use it for any other purpose.
Analytics
Google Analytics:
We use Google Analytics to track and monitor the use of the App. You can opt-out of certain Google Analytics features through your mobile device settings or by following Google's instructions.
Advertising
AdMob by Google
:
We display ads using AdMob by Google, which may collect information to show relevant advertisements. You can opt-out by visiting Google's Ads Settings page.
10. Behavioral Remarketing
We use remarketing services to advertise on third-party websites to you after you visited our service. This is done by using cookies that track your past interaction with the App.
Google Ads (AdWords):
Provided by Google Inc. You can customize your ads and opt-out using Google’s Ads Settings page.
Facebook Remarketing:
You can opt-out from Facebook’s interest-based ads using Facebook’s provided instructions.
11. Protection Against Malware and Network Abuse
Malware Protection:
The App is regularly scanned for malware or malicious code to ensure user safety. We recommend downloading the App from trusted sources like the Google Play Store.
Network Abuse
:
The App does not engage in any form of network abuse, such as unauthorized data transmission, spamming, or excessive use of network resources.
12. Children’s Privacy
This App is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.
13. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page.
14. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us:
App Name:
Beauty Camera - AI Photo Editor
Developer Name:
Kamrej Apps
Email:
kamrejapps@gmail.com
